1006
01:31:56,505 --> 01:31:58,382
Što god želiš.

1007
01:32:00,759 --> 01:32:02,351
Obećaj.

1008
01:32:04,638 --> 01:32:06,310
Obećavam.

1009
01:32:50,602 --> 01:32:52,433
Oh, Meg.

1010
01:32:58,235 --> 01:32:59,714
Umrla je.

1011
01:34:18,484 --> 01:34:20,076
Hej.

1012
01:34:20,320 --> 01:34:23,357
Sjećaš li se te žene, Rene?

1013
01:34:23,740 --> 01:34:25,332
Socijalne radnice?

1014
01:34:25,867 --> 01:34:27,186
Da.

1015
01:34:28,286 --> 01:34:30,481
Mislim da bi je
trebali posjetiti.

1016
01:34:31,247 --> 01:34:32,441
Zašto?

1017
01:34:33,875 --> 01:34:37,550
